{"tid":1867213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(極重要) 依家死亡率計法可能有問題，勿輕視","createTime":"2020-02-07T05:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T08:42:48.000Z","uid":67043,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3abe6dc2debcf9c35958d06cffa86d0733811379","tid":1867213,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"一個感染係要經過幾個階段<br />\n感染&gt;&gt;潛伏期&gt;&gt;發病&gt;&gt;死亡/康復<br />\n<br />\n依家公怖既死亡率係以現時死亡人數除以總感染人數嚟計，但呢個計法係唔能夠完全反映個事實。因為所有病者唔係同一時間發病，佢哋所處既階段都唔一致。呢隻病毒潛伏期+發病既時間都幾長，但感染人數上升得快。用依家既感染人數嚟除其實變相會沖淡咗死亡率，正確少少既做法應該用死亡既人嚟除返幾日至十日前既感染人數，得出嚟既死亡率一定高過依家2%<br />\n<br />\n另外我建議大家應該要更注意係個康復率<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fc6RpxF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffc6RpxF.jpg&h=1b9e1ee9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n按照佢哋依家計算死亡率既方法嚟計算康復率 (用7/2 13:00數據)<br />\n康復:1,582<br />\n確診:31,215<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">康復率暫時係得5%</span><br />\n<br />\n所以啲藍屍話美國流感都死好多人，依家個死亡率唔高可以唔駛擔心。你可以同佢講美國流感感染人數係好多，計返死亡率唔高，同埋人哋流感康復率高！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但你中咗武漢肺炎康復率係5%炸</span>"},{"pid":"5b73dc30bf229885686d529b2da4b3194f652230","tid":1867213,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:51:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ce499b8cf7af948b1bc7bd56347aac16720c498c","tid":1867213,"uid":102700,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:53:22.000Z","msg":"藍尸: 2%死亡率 即係98%康復率"},{"pid":"d3c270a325339ff38e86419427c0f4c76c5c9926","tid":1867213,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:53:22.000Z","msg":"大陸唔使睇，睇海外暫時未大量死亡"},{"pid":"21a21ef75d7cf77183efb68286eec208d83f2f13","tid":1867213,"uid":167289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:53:33.000Z","msg":"直情有問題啦<br />\n而家好似assume 咗啲人一惹到個病毒就即刻會瓜咁"},{"pid":"2033ae853b2b8170808de2c0349e6033ea18a7c6","tid":1867213,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:54:43.000Z","msg":"睇左幾日已經唔信d數字<br />\n有隱形病人<br />\n死係屋企<br />\n死係街<br />\n未確診死"},{"pid":"9535d614bfdbbfe3a1ccbd83dfff898315579aa7","tid":1867213,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:55:16.000Z","msg":"特別係李文亮都保唔住，就知幾撚大穫"},{"pid":"3b449439f22d1c573cab4e58f6c2633d02c5a34a","tid":1867213,"uid":271857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:03:16.000Z","msg":"大陸公佈嘅數字X5至X10 倍。"},{"pid":"cf80ddcbb1e5b124895183d163c1d23d0213fdac","tid":1867213,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b449439f22d1c573cab4e58f6c2633d02c5a34a","tid":1867213,"uid":271857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:03:16.000Z","msg":"大陸公佈嘅數字X5至X10 倍。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:08:37.000Z","msg":"冇錯...康復率5%係假設佢數據正確<br />\n但大陸基本上係報細數，即係個康復率仲會低好多"},{"pid":"bf47321090560a29f54a861e8465407079869328","tid":1867213,"uid":216113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:16:55.000Z","msg":"日日個死亡率都係2.1% 你都重信佢？"},{"pid":"9bae9078b1200f8cbd4daa8bdeb665e42a460dbe","tid":1867213,"uid":321374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:21:21.000Z","msg":"大陸條數假既<br />\n唔好曬精神時間"},{"pid":"2024920ea747b49b30adcb93ebf2c563dc385e8b","tid":1867213,"uid":45089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:29:24.000Z","msg":"要將確診case 同死亡個案case by case link 埋先準..."},{"pid":"4092b69f7ff72dbac85c3be10eae136eca15fead","tid":1867213,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf47321090560a29f54a861e8465407079869328","tid":1867213,"uid":216113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:16:55.000Z","msg":"日日個死亡率都係2.1% 你都重信佢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T07:55:20.000Z","msg":"造假康復率都係得5%....真實情況可想而知"},{"pid":"ea27dfedd465a4f1c443e684d3a3c5988c35f5c3","tid":1867213,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2024920ea747b49b30adcb93ebf2c563dc385e8b","tid":1867213,"uid":45089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:29:24.000Z","msg":"要將確診case 同死亡個案case by case link 埋先準..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T07:56:34.000Z","msg":"冇錯....條數造假大家都知, 但計算方法都係一個問題"},{"pid":"83546abd1118d6061a4226029ac974a1a09c2de6","tid":1867213,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2024920ea747b49b30adcb93ebf2c563dc385e8b","tid":1867213,"uid":45089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:29:24.000Z","msg":"要將確診case 同死亡個案case by case link 埋先準..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:01:39.000Z","msg":"死亡嘅一定確診<br />\n<br />\n理論上你拎個死亡pool 出黎，除確診數字，就係目前染病後，outcome 為死亡嘅機率。不過呢個pool 代表唔到general population."},{"pid":"b6d0e3c6a5ee5a079a358e319415e3750e6096f1","tid":1867213,"uid":50310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"21a21ef75d7cf77183efb68286eec208d83f2f13","tid":1867213,"uid":167289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:53:33.000Z","msg":"直情有問題啦<br />\n而家好似assume 咗啲人一惹到個病毒就即刻會瓜咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:04:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">中國式</span>防疫方法：<br />\n病你唔死、餓9死你<br />\n然後，唔計入死亡人數度！<br />\n幾<span style=\"color: red;\">富有強國特色</span>統計方法得架！<br />\n真係屌你都廢事<br />\n{唔推}"},{"pid":"2f7dbafe7e8f2de5e483247e7a784a3c147685ec","tid":1867213,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:06:19.000Z","msg":"廣東今日先第一個人死，叫人點信呢條數啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a531a5fcf5327873a71df469415ebf3abca08a5f","tid":1867213,"uid":129378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f7dbafe7e8f2de5e483247e7a784a3c147685ec","tid":1867213,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:06:19.000Z","msg":"廣東今日先第一個人死，叫人點信呢條數啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:08:06.000Z","msg":"呢個真, 武漢D人死到哀鴻遍野，廣東竟然先死一件，好唔可信"},{"pid":"616037fead8423f67a789caaa3ecf81a8090ba